      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, i need help writing a formal email to an employee. they've been showing up about 15 mins late to every shift for the last two weeks straight. i need it to sound professional and firm so they know it's a real issue, but not like i'm attacking them personally. can u draft something?",
